{"type": "article", "id": 63049, "title": "把电视“隐藏“起来，还可以用来听音乐｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-04-17T22:58:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 57967, "name": "Bert Frank"}, {"id": 57968, "name": "Mayice Studio"}, {"id": 49879, "name": "GANDIABLASCO"}, {"id": 57969, "name": "Chunmi Design"}, {"id": 14845, "name": "Foster + Partners"}, {"id": 683, "name": "LG"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 80, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190417205919DFaUrbzIGqu8nRiY.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Signature OLED TV R by Foster + Partners for LG</h3><p>LG 最近与设计公司 Foster+Partners 合作，在 2019 年米兰设计周推出全球第一款可滚动电视 Signature OLED TV R 。</p><p>它有三种不同的模式，让用户决定屏幕的大小。Foster+Partners 设计了电视的外部几何结构和表面处理，并积极参与创建特定的内部机制。</p><p>Signature OLED TV R 的设计意图是想让电视轻松“隐藏”。滚动到它底部的盒子里。三种查看模式包括线视图，其中显示将下拉，以便仅显示面板的四分之一。用户可以从时钟、相框、心情、音乐和家庭仪表板等功能中进行选择。调用时钟模式，查看时间和天气一瞥或帧模式，享受从智能手机或心情模式共享的家庭照片，创造一个更轻松的氛围。用户仍然可以在屏幕上控制音乐，并可以选择在此模式下控制智能家居小工具。</p><p>即便是完全“隐藏”起来的状态，用户也可以欣赏音乐和其他音频内容。全视图提供大屏幕观看体验。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210019Z7sz2IHfLgFvPD9V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562694\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210019x2erTbPvdOJhcgQE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019041721002034vAlih2y9Wqx1Nn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662014\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210020qHEPdhKMNT82lnjF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904172100212SAcCux6QHlDg1ez.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502961\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/04/16/foster-partners-lg-roll-up-tv/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Warm of Year by Chunmi Design</h3><p>把时间融入到工作日常当中平常的事物，从点滴当中找到生活的温度。把毫无关联的两件事物联系在一起，创造出属于生活当中的小小惊喜就是这本日历设计的初衷。</p><p>温暖日历将杯垫背面设计成 12 个月份日期，通过勾画简单便捷记录生活工作。杯垫的正面通过变化的四季颜色也在无形中提醒着时间的推移与变化，小小杯垫的两面，一面是充满生活温度的感性，一面是充满时间规划的理性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210108FcfBC5H4WLo0wi6z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210108yYhdaqZHBuglkUwE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210109mizLDeYWF6fOkSQd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210109Wo4ivwVhIxy90tUM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210109TO3ZGD2qKcxupF1N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904172101108SNJvuWmqPFzCVT5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210110lTgr3BkI9QoiVsOJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>BUIT Collection by Mayice Studio </h3><p>BUIT 是 Mayice Studio 为 GANDIABLASCO 品牌新设计的户外家具系列。马德里 Mayice Studio 是由建筑师 Marta Alonso Yebra与 Imanol Calderón Elósegui 于 2014 创立的一家多学科设计工作室，他们致力于室内设计项目和家具、产品设计，其作品在纽约、柏林、米兰等城市设计周中均有展出。</p><p>在创作中，他们喜欢与当地的工匠及妇女合作，对材料与生产工艺进行细致地研究。Mayice studio 和 GANDIABLASCO 一样，喜欢使用优质材料，极其注重加工处理、组合和完成过程中的细节，同时也非常尊重传统，他们以过去与现在之间的对话为原则，将传统与新型材料结合起来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210205k971SWjDTduIhM8O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210206WxkayMpKvTHcItfd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210206HbP9SkdxRFDOCqfB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210206iUb2QnqjBrVcMNuO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210207YHN1XQDhO8zfG6IF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210207tUz8sJg1oQpchZ4I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904172102078VaE5B1JjbXSR2Oo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210208qibs085IRyazFfet.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Unimaru by Usagi No Nedoko</h3><p>我们之前介绍过设计师 Koichi Yoshimura 在日本京都创立的品牌 Sola Cube，将各植物制作成透明立体的生命标本。</p><p>最近，它们又将目光转向海胆，试图借助其千变万化的外壳图案，做成装饰物。</p><p>整个系列名为 Unimaru，收集了世界各地的稀有海胆品种，包括马粪海胆、光棘海胆、叶棘头帕海胆与梅氏长海胆，利用液态丙烯酸制成透明外壳，创作出精致独一无二的透明的标本。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210259BZNLptSR2AEWxez5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904172103008GAH6m7fIKN5V30d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019041721030072sfN3wVTPgM9m8F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210300tQHFZGW8EX2b7Vrp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210300tCTPdBKNUpzyGeMk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210301GRQLcs2i4bk9dyKa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210301bFsqtmQAPHaG2DdI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210301efms1gP70RrM6hz2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Flagon, Spate, Rote, Rift, Trave, and Tanto by Bert Frank</h3><p>Bert Frank 是 2013 年由设计师 Robbie Llewellyn 和金属制品工厂创始人 Adam Yeats 创立的一个屡获殊荣的英国豪华照明品牌。</p><p>最近，它们在米兰设计周上展示了新的照明解决方案，所有产品都是在英国设计和制造，新品灵感源自装饰艺术风格和工业美学，呈现出极简迷人的特质。</p><p>一直很受欢迎的 Flagon 枝形吊灯经过重新设计升级为 Flagon Three Light Cluster，三个 Flagon 吊灯悬挂在一个三角吊具板上。</p><p>Spate 可作为吊灯、壁灯和台灯使用。它的圆润形状是对装饰艺术风格的致敬，大理石球体、黄铜金属制品和蛋白石玻璃罩的组合。</p><p>Rote 有四种版本可供选择：吊灯、壁灯、台灯和枝形吊灯，它由开槽的激光切割金刚石叶片制成，与黄铜和黑色几何叶子的发光黄铜环相连。</p><p>Rift 既有壁灯又有吊灯。它的蛋白石玻璃球可以柔化光线，营造出温暖的光泽，平静和舒适的氛围。Trave 可作为吊灯、台灯或壁灯，试图表达装饰艺术的魅力。</p><p>Tanto 采用纤薄、极简的外形，配有两个不对称黄铜棒和 White Carrera 大理石连接的圆柱形蛋白石灯，呈现出雕塑般的外观。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210346WxvimhSwnuFVaAG1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210346deL4IWkBPGyo60UX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210346TkX2AdRvwCUtW195.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210346NDnl08X9ux6YeqHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.587500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210347cM7JdhIEoGuDjxUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.418519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904172103485iCWXyObTv0B39UQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.556790\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210349dC8pxfYsSUNgoAtu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.446914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190417210350VTzLbJSqKmGZWv1E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.566667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.bertfrank.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bert Frank</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>"}